Hi all,

I highly agree with Ron Salmon.  I have put 3,000 miles on a set of 
Hankooks in the past week.  Even driving through Wyoming on I-80 with 
wind gusts to 45 mph, my loaded 76 Westy was stable and steady at 70 
mph.  They are GREAT tires!

